Wave 9a polish on the Set Action dialog: validation icons now expose their accessibleName as a hover toolTip; opening the dialog drops focus straight into the typing widget (Simple text / regex / numeric value / Top-N spinbox) per current mode instead of the field combo; both regex and Simple text inputs gain a native × clear button; clicking the `[abc]` cheatsheet chip selects the inner "abc" so the next keystroke replaces them; Ctrl+Enter triggers Apply from anywhere in the dialog; and Alt-letter mnemonics fire the action buttons — Alt+A Apply, Alt+C Close, Alt+R Recent, Alt+S Switch to Regex, Alt+W reset Window size (#348, #350).
